Author: comicsansmasterfont
Text: Woooow that doesn’t even come across as one of those well-meaning “you look so h E a L t H y” comments, she actually just straight up insulted you. I suggest that you take this “friend” and place them directly in a the smelliest dumpster you can find. Then go home and eat whatever the fuck you want because this rotten trash person has exactly zero opinions that matter.
